  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-38 is-title1-48 is-title-bold is-upper\" style=\"text-align:left;\">幾何之內無帝王路<br />\n～但要走在正確的道路上</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">數學的學習有正確的道路，但是沒有輕鬆的捷徑。<br />\n應該學習舉一反十的思維模式，而不是扼殺興趣的機械刷題。<br />\n這些傑出的獵豹學子，都在正確的道路上不畏困難，堅持目標地奮鬥多年。<br />\n他們其中有好幾位在獵豹參與了不只一種課程（J,S,FS,Sci,FA,AMC…)<br />\n—-</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\">真有「高效率的學習」嗎？<br />\n獵豹的 專家模式 用一半的題量 超越兩倍的效率!!<br />\n12/28 (六) AM 10:30，高中數學S直播講座 宗翰老師 主講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">#按讚留言+1參加</span></strong><br />\n<a attributionsrc=\"https://www.cheetahstem.com/privacy_sandbox/comet/register/source/?xt=AZWUFSnXLvt4Pz1gd-W0WJ2Tvf_ZRPQQ5CqSfakEgK-SjADeJm1vc4lCrr8AoUc21cDhx7m-GGy--eWbl9OhDiTtL4Ag5Y70rrefxUeJS16UGdB6Ehuxe2RJ7iKs5gxfZdnH2-dzRd_t1PCAkqNyP1TchB_LNcVQa1I5JpnVFIvPj8T1IJ4y5A4vA4Dbfd9TkLm9gu2n_U-vv1xbSSok9P7BUBdJsu3dMIYfmoVaHgy4pxCUYtFCiQ4aoBCzW_Z6yY57w-eiUw5-TkdBrq14kbCj5iF1dZZos7SgKjXADJWtiUdwP13ArlNKBbv5tIMSCQ2w0JKt_rIz1g050zmwZhIZjldZaBeLmOCJa1TzoOvF74JWQAJ3XWYD8Pka3YJAQhkcrnAzlX4eKKZ6-nDdXblYKSn2H3xYGZiclxxrzJJG2lJB2qL5nla0nXixDe75Jy-NlRBTTkRbx4BnpkqYIAFgqLm4BPsCD88aFx2niMQ-9ODWnFSfJHwrRR-vH5_Vn7RFfxywqDV2NUppaGGs5g1-g9WO3TiPM6MHBDI28xOzRYoWpEBqUwCWvoZFps7OtKLMdqwWUHshlhxOIKJw-OsTgelOe56aefPY8SXUyXEB29QfTxmvGmrnJxAMXGHqvdiuO5pnip_WnkgUMNHXsJHVf47xiB5P82oKb-fVm0LsoytZe6if928WJbVaIoGcAQO4qqrQdP298x34DbpY5QK_w7s2rF4XJj8Ij_qgXvkDX1Mv7sJxkuPpqcc91ZOcUlOZ-gym6kwSAfoeayYhKh2fx-m3V2ozpNxsY1rDXU2P1MiOLnou22aRmnGk7waD-7HL2ldPQwlAmrec2C67oYIFyBQKtVdstqZQWDFYNS1hZfCM1t1HX7JS9a1jzz9KIJtq66ZiM10M8LdwN6xNOZwp\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/posts/1638303400455672/?__cft__[0]=AZXGL9cFZPGA49tfv2zSJ1Y3Q9r2WgtTFac6INgOur900Z